news.title: Pune: Houses soon for PMAY beneficiaries in Wadgaon Khurd
news.para: The review of project works was carried out by a delegation of the Pune Municipal Corporation (PMC) officials on Thursday.

news.title: Nashik civic body to levy additional taxes on 1.3 lakh property owners
news.para: The civic administration is now in the process of serving show cause notices to these property owners and then the hearings will be conducted.

news.title: Unique ID number for Meerut properties
news.para: ​There are several properties and houses which don't have any number. These houses will be covered under the GIS survey for the generation of unique property ID.
